title: Cassie Is Stepping Back Into The Real World!
description:
Cassie has been justifiably very cautious with how much time she and her family spends in public during the pandemic. But she's got some good news! Her toddler Hazel is now FULLY vaccinated, so the fam is ready to dip their toes back into the Real World! 
She'll talk about the memories they made last week at Stone Mountain's Pumpkin Festival.
